ox-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">     ② </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">본교 홈페이지 </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">→ </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">재학생 </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">→ </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">강의계획서</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">     ③ </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">본교 홈페이지 </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">→ </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">학사</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">/</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">생활</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">/</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">장학 </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">→ </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">시간표 및 강의계획서</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"> 다<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>주의사항</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\">  - 대기신청 진행하지 않음</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\">  - 예비수강신청한 내역은 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">‘</span>연습<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">’</span>개념으로<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">실제 수강신청내역에 반영되지 않습니다</span></u></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\">    반드시 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">본 신청 기간</span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">(05.13.(</span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">수</span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">)~05.15.(</span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\">금</span></u><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\">)) </span></u></span></span><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 500;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">내에 수강신청 완료</span></span>해야</span></u>합니다<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">.</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\">  - 다른 학생들도 연습이 가능하도록<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">수강신청 연습한 내역은 바로 삭제</span></u>해 주시기바랍니다<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. (</span>미삭제 내역은<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, 수강신청 기간 전에</span> 일괄 삭제됨<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">)</span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"hwpEditorBoardContent\" style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'> </div>\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'> </div>\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\">문의 : 학사지원팀 ☎ 02)2260-3699/3700</span></span></div>",
